    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Mr. [**Known lastname 8498**] is a 73 yoM on HD-anuric, h/o AFib not currently o",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s1",
      "text": "Mr. [**Known lastname 8498**] is a 73 yoM on HD-anuric, h/o AFib not currently on    coumadin (though is on at home), who is being transferred from the    neurology service for respiratory distress and hypoxia."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He was    admitted on [**2191-8-12**] after a fall resulting in acute on chronic",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s2",
      "text": "He was    admitted on [**2191-8-12**] after a fall resulting in acute on chronic SDH on    the left; his course is complicated by seizure and he has been started    on fosphenytoin & phenytoin.    ."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "This evening he was noted to be in acute respiratory distress with    desats to ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s3",
      "text": "This evening he was noted to be in acute respiratory distress with    desats to the low to mid 90's on 3LNC (reportedly desatting to the mid    70's on room air; has had a variable O2 requirement since being    admitted)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His blood pressure dropped to the 70's systolic and was    responsive to the 80'",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s4",
      "text": "His blood pressure dropped to the 70's systolic and was    responsive to the 80's and then 100's after a 250 cc NS bolus.  he was    febrile to 101.9,concern was aspiration event,pt has been on on    vanco/genta for the given recent fevers,with neg cultures     he was briefly in MICU green on [**8-17**] - [**8-18**] for fevers and hypotension    to the 70's."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Respiratory failure, acute (not ARDS/[**Doctor Last Name 2**])    Assessment:   ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s5",
      "text": "Respiratory failure, acute (not ARDS/[**Doctor Last Name 2**])    Assessment:    Remains vented on ACx18/500/40%/5."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "LS diminished at bases.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s6",
      "text": "LS diminished at bases."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Sats    94-97% Pt sedated on fentanyl and versed drips.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s7",
      "text": "Sats    94-97% Pt sedated on fentanyl and versed drips."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He is able to follow    commands inconsistently.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s8",
      "text": "He is able to follow    commands inconsistently."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Action:    Suctioned for thick copious secretions q 2-4 hours.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s9",
      "text": "Action:    Suctioned for thick copious secretions q 2-4 hours."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:10",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Response:    No change.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s10",
      "text": "Response:    No change."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row598031:11",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt maintaining good saturation    Plan:    Wean vent as tolerated.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row598031#s11",
      "text": "Pt maintaining good saturation    Plan:    Wean vent as tolerated."
    },
    {
